ClrHome
Disp "PROMPT?
Input Str1
Disp "MATH?
Input Str2
0->N
Asm(prgmCHAT)
Disp "WAITING...
Pause N
1->P
Lbl A
ClrHome
If P=1
Disp Str3
If P=2
Disp Str4
If P=3
Disp Str5
If P=4
Disp Str6
If P=5
Disp Str7
If P=6
Disp Str8
If P=7
Disp Str9
If P=8
Disp Str0
Output(8,1,P
Output(8,2,"/
Output(8,3,N
Output(8,13,"<>
Repeat K=24 or K=26 or K=45
getKey->K
End
If K=24 and P>1
P-1->P
If K=26 and P<N
P+1->P
If K=45
Return
Goto A
